<div>
  <div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "jakeday.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: "profile-img" %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class"progress">
              <div
                class="progress-bar"
                role="progressbar"
                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                aria-valuemin="0"
                aria-valuemax="100"
                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%; height: 20px; text-align: center;"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Hello...</p>
        <p>My name is Jake Day and my passion is building software products for small businesses and startups. I also create design and programming videos and books which have been viewed and read by over 3 million people. You can find out more about my education and project history below.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#productHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="productHistory"
          >
            Products
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#educationHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="educationHistory"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>


        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Allmoxy - Developer and technical support for manufacturing automation software.
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Nav - Backend Ruby on Rails developer for finance software.
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Wild Academy - Instructor and Founder. Online programming and design courses.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="productHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <%= link_to "Wild Academy", "https://www.wildacademy.com/" %>
              Online videos and text based courses on programming and design.
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <%= link_to "SketchUp Hero", "http://sketchuphero.com/" %>
              SketchUp Hero is a beginner friendly video and text based course that will teach you how to use SketchUp for personal and professional projects.
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              My Books
              <%= link_to "Learn Ruby", "https://www.amazon.com/Learn-Ruby-Beginner-Introduction-Programming-ebook/dp/B00R4T8EJ4" %>
              <%= link_to "Learn PHP", "https://www.amazon.com/Learn-PHP-Beginner-Introduction-Programming-ebook/dp/B00ULKOU1O/" %>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="educationHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              DPL's University of Utah Web Design and Development Academy - Full Stack Ruby on Rails
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
